articles.title: Europe’s biggest economy shrank in the third quarter - CNN
articles.description: Output in Germany fell in the third quarter, increasing the risk of a recession in Europe’s biggest economy.
articles.content:
Output in Germany fell in the third quarter, official data showed Monday, increasing the risk of a recession in Europes biggest economy.
